# `myoptions.h` diagnostics section is append-only

When editing `myoptions.h`, **never remove or rename anything** in the `/* DIAGNOSTICS */` section (currently lines ~202–229).

- Do not delete existing defines (even if commented out)
- Do not delete existing comments/headers/separators
- Only add new diagnostics toggles beneath the existing ones, or add new commented defines without removing old ones

